{"type":"message","id":"bbeb7e3f","parentId":"47dd6ed3","timestamp":"2026-02-24T12:11:02.804Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-02-24 17:41 GMT+5:30] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: Initialize AGENT RESEARCHER: Scrape and structure public scheme and budget data from data.gov.in, state portals, PMJDY/PMAY/MNREGA, GeM/eProcurement, RTI datasets, and budget PDFs. Output JSON, pipeline: Scraper -> Cleaner -> Structurer -> Database. Output example: {\"scheme_name\":\"PM Awas Yojana\",\"income_limit\":300000,\"location_type\":\"rural\",\"documents_required\":[\"aadhaar\",\"income certificate\"],\"budget_allocated\":5000000000}"}],"timestamp":1771935062800}}
